import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'
import { FaBars } from 'react-icons/fa'
import { Nav, NavbarContainer, NavLogo, MobileIcon, NavMenu, NavItem, NavLinks, NavBtn, NavBtnLink} from './HeaderElements'

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <Nav>
      <NavbarContainer>
        <NavLogo >Indielog</NavLogo>
        <MobileIcon>
          <FaBars />
        </MobileIcon>
        <NavMenu>
          <NavItem>
            <NavLinks >聽聽音樂</NavLinks>
          </NavItem>
          <NavItem>
            <NavLinks >聊聊音樂</NavLinks>
          </NavItem>
        </NavMenu>
        <NavBtn>
          <NavBtnLink >Sign in</NavBtnLink>
        </NavBtn>
      </NavbarContainer>
    </Nav>
  )
}

export default Header;
